<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: advanced warcaskets -->
  <VFEP_AdvancedWarcaskets.label>进阶型无畏战棺</VFEP_AdvancedWarcaskets.label>
  <!-- EN: Construct improved variations of warcaskets which lean towards speed, protection or a balanced approach. -->
  <VFEP_AdvancedWarcaskets.description>解锁组装性能更强的进阶型无畏战棺。</VFEP_AdvancedWarcaskets.description>
  <!-- EN:
    <li>subject->warcasket evolution</li>
    <li>subject_story->refined warcasket designs for speed, durability, and versatility, setting new standards in mechanized warfare</li>
    <li>subject_story->crafted war machines that danced in battlefields with lethal grace</li>
    <li>subject_story->balanced the trinity of speed, protection, and firepower in a symphony of destruction</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->enhancing the anatomy of war</li>
  -->
  <VFEP_AdvancedWarcaskets.generalRules.rulesStrings>  
    <li>subject->无畏战棺迭代</li>
    <li>subject_story->改进了无畏战棺的速度、耐久和多功能性，为机械化战争制定了新准则</li>
    <li>subject_story->制造了能在战场上跳起死亡之舞的战争机器</li>
    <li>subject_story->在毁灭的交响乐中平衡速度、防护与火力</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->加强对战场局势的解析</li>
  </VFEP_AdvancedWarcaskets.generalRules.rulesStrings>
    
  <!-- EN: spacer warcaskets -->
  <VFEP_SpacerWarcaskets.label>太空时代无畏战棺</VFEP_SpacerWarcaskets.label>
  <!-- EN: Manufacture Spacer-era warcaskets - a pinacle of war technology. -->
  <VFEP_SpacerWarcaskets.description>解锁组装太空时代科技级别的无畏战棺。</VFEP_SpacerWarcaskets.description>
  <!-- EN:
    <li>subject->pinnacle of mechanized warfare</li>
    <li>subject_story->crafted warcaskets that harnessed spacer-era technology, embodying the zenith of military engineering</li>
    <li>subject_story->merged the cutting edge of space-age tech with the ancient art of war, creating unparalleled battle machines</li>
    <li>subject_story->redefined the battlefield with warcaskets that were legends incarnate</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->achieving the apex of combat evolution</li>
  -->
  <VFEP_SpacerWarcaskets.generalRules.rulesStrings>  
    <li>subject->机械化战争的尖端成果</li>
    <li>subject_story->利用太空时代技术制造了新一代战棺，展现了军事工程学的顶峰</li>
    <li>subject_story->创造出了融合太空时代科技顶尖成果和远古战争技艺的伟大作战机器</li>
    <li>subject_story->通过传说的化身无畏战棺重新定义了战场</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->努力达到战斗进化的顶点</li>
  </VFEP_SpacerWarcaskets.generalRules.rulesStrings>

  <!-- EN: spacer warcasket weaponry -->
  <VFEP_SpacerWarcasketWeaponry.label>太空时代无畏战棺武器</VFEP_SpacerWarcasketWeaponry.label>
  <!-- EN: Utilise new spacer technologies to create upscaled weapons designed to be mounted on warcaskets. -->
  <VFEP_SpacerWarcasketWeaponry.description>解锁建造与无畏战棺配套使用的太空时代科技级别武器。</VFEP_SpacerWarcasketWeaponry.description>
  <!-- EN:
    <li>subject->spacer-grade armaments</li>
    <li>subject_story->harnessed the mysteries of spacer tech to craft weapons of unrivaled potency for warcaskets</li>
    <li>subject_story->ushered in an era where warcaskets wielded the power to alter the course of wars with a single shot</li>
    <li>subject_story->married the art of war to the science of the stars, creating armaments born of the cosmos</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->wielding the stars' wrath</li>
  -->
  <VFEP_SpacerWarcasketWeaponry.generalRules.rulesStrings>  
    <li>subject->太空时代军备</li>
    <li>subject_story->利用太空时代科技的奥秘，为无畏战棺制造出性能极其出色的武器</li>
    <li>subject_story->引领了一个无畏战棺只开一枪就能改变战争方向的时代</li>
    <li>subject_story->将战争技艺与星际科学融合，创造出源于宇宙的军备</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->运用着群星之怒</li>
  </VFEP_SpacerWarcasketWeaponry.generalRules.rulesStrings>

  <!-- EN: specialised warcaskets -->
  <VFEP_SpecialisedWarcaskets.label>特化型无畏战棺</VFEP_SpecialisedWarcaskets.label>
  <!-- EN: Manufacture warcaskets designed to fit specialized roles. -->
  <VFEP_SpecialisedWarcaskets.description>解锁组装特点鲜明的特化型无畏战棺。</VFEP_SpecialisedWarcaskets.description>
  <!-- EN:
    <li>subject->custom combat solutions</li>
    <li>subject_story->designed warcaskets with specialized roles, from silent assassins to unstoppable juggernauts</li>
    <li>subject_story->broke the mold of traditional warfare, introducing units tailored for specific tactical needs</li>
    <li>subject_story->elevated the warcasket program to new heights with bespoke war machines</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->specializing the gears of war</li>
  -->
  <VFEP_SpecialisedWarcaskets.generalRules.rulesStrings>  
    <li>subject->定制战斗方案</li>
    <li>subject_story->设计了静谧刺客、无畏勇士等定位特化的无畏战棺</li>
    <li>subject_story->打破了传统的作战方式，引入为特殊战术需求而量身定制的单位</li>
    <li>subject_story->用定制化的战争机器将无畏战棺项目推向新高度</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->醉心研究战争装备</li>
  </VFEP_SpecialisedWarcaskets.generalRules.rulesStrings>

  <!-- EN: sweat fermentation -->
  <VFEP_SweatFermentation.label>汗液发酵</VFEP_SweatFermentation.label>
  <!-- EN: Craft suits which combine alcohol distillation and nutrient paste synthesis to produce rum from recycled human waste. -->
  <VFEP_SweatFermentation.description>将酒精提纯与营养膏合成科技相结合，解锁制作能利用人类体液生产朗姆酒的「朗姆酒套装」。</VFEP_SweatFermentation.description>
  <!-- EN:
    <li>subject->biochemical ingenuity</li>
    <li>subject_story->turned the cycle of waste into a source of sustenance and spirit, crafting rum from the sweat of toil</li>
    <li>subject_story->blurred the lines between distillation and desperation, finding innovation in the unconventional</li>
    <li>subject_story->created a self-sustaining cycle of work, waste, and whiskey, fueling both body and morale</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->brewing resilience from refuse</li>
  -->
  <VFEP_SweatFermentation.generalRules.rulesStrings>  
    <li>subject->生化独创力</li>
    <li>subject_story->将人体的排泄物循环利用以转化为营养与烈酒，用辛劳的汗水酿造朗姆酒</li>
    <li>subject_story->模糊了蒸馏与绝望间的界限，通过非常规方法寻求创新</li>
    <li>subject_story->创造了一种工作→排泄物→朗姆酒的自循环体系，以此促动身体与精神</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->用排泄物酿造美酒</li>
  </VFEP_SweatFermentation.generalRules.rulesStrings>

  <!-- EN: warcasket removal -->
  <VFEP_WarcasketRemoval.label>无畏战棺卸除</VFEP_WarcasketRemoval.label>
  <!-- EN: Unlocks the operation “remove warcasket” to remove a pawn from a warcasket, losing both their arms and legs, and reducing the warcasket to slag. -->
  <VFEP_WarcasketRemoval.description>解锁能够卸除无畏战棺的特殊手术。接受手术的殖民者会失去四肢，而无畏战棺的机体也将变成可回收的钢渣块。</VFEP_WarcasketRemoval.description>
  <!-- EN:
    <li>subject->the cost of war</li>
    <li>subject_story->developed techniques to reclaim warriors from their metal confines, a bittersweet victory over the machine</li>
    <li>subject_story->faced the grim reality of extracting the human core from the war machine, sacrificing limb for life</li>
    <li>subject_story->turned the promise of mechanized might into the pain of loss, with every warcasket removal a reminder of war's toll</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->unraveling the bond between flesh and steel</li>
  -->
  <VFEP_WarcasketRemoval.generalRules.rulesStrings>  
    <li>subject->战争的代价</li>
    <li>subject_story->研发了将战士们从“金属棺材”中解放出来的技术，这是对抗机器的惨痛胜利</li>
    <li>subject_story->面对必须牺牲肢体才能将人从战争机器中解放出来的残酷事实</li>
    <li>subject_story->将机械化之力的承诺转变为失去的痛苦，每次卸除无畏战棺都会警示人们战争所带来的伤亡</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->解除血肉与钢铁间的联系</li>
  </VFEP_WarcasketRemoval.generalRules.rulesStrings> 

  <!-- EN: warcaskets -->
  <VFEP_Warcaskets.label>基础型无畏战棺</VFEP_Warcaskets.label>
  <!-- EN: Build warcasket foundries to manufacture basic warcasket parts and outfit pawns to utilise said warcaskets. -->
  <VFEP_Warcaskets.description>解锁建造「无畏战棺铸造厂」，你可以用它来组装最基础的无畏战棺。</VFEP_Warcaskets.description>
  <!-- EN:
    <li>subject->mechanized infantry development</li>
    <li>subject_story->initiated the age of warcaskets, transforming foot soldiers into titans on the battlefield</li>
    <li>subject_story->mastered the art of warcasket manufacturing, melding metal and might into a singular force</li>
    <li>subject_story->ushered in a new era of warfare, where the line between man and machine blurred</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->pioneering the future of combat</li>
  -->
  <VFEP_Warcaskets.generalRules.rulesStrings>  
    <li>subject->机械化步兵的研发</li>
    <li>subject_story->将步兵变为战场上的主宰，开创了无畏战棺的时代</li>
    <li>subject_story->掌握了铸造无畏战棺的技艺，将金属与血肉合为一种奇特的力量</li>
    <li>subject_story->模糊人与机器间的界限，引领了战争的新时代</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->开创未来战斗的新形式</li>
  </VFEP_Warcaskets.generalRules.rulesStrings>

  <!-- EN: warcasket weaponry -->
  <VFEP_WarcasketWeaponry.label>无畏战棺武器</VFEP_WarcasketWeaponry.label>
  <!-- EN: Build upscaled weapons designed to be mounted on warcaskets. -->
  <VFEP_WarcasketWeaponry.description>解锁建造与无畏战棺配套使用的高级武器。</VFEP_WarcasketWeaponry.description>
  <!-- EN:
    <li>subject->armament innovation</li>
    <li>subject_story->engineered devastating weaponry for warcaskets, turning them into walking arsenals</li>
    <li>subject_story->bridged the gap between artillery power and infantry flexibility</li>
    <li>subject_story->granted warcaskets the firepower to decimate, defend, and dominate</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->arming the giants of war</li>
  -->
  <VFEP_WarcasketWeaponry.generalRules.rulesStrings>  
    <li>subject->军备革新</li>
    <li>subject_story->为无畏战棺制造了威力惊人的武器，将其变为移动军械库</li>
    <li>subject_story->弥补了火炮威力与步兵灵活性之间的差距</li>
    <li>subject_story->让无畏战棺获得用于杀戮、防御以及支配的火力</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->武装战争巨人</li>
  </VFEP_WarcasketWeaponry.generalRules.rulesStrings>

</LanguageData>